a-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1504:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1504\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1504-TW</a>)、永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>)、台灣虎航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6757:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6757\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6757-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
